You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
Well, here we are in the kitchen. The room is well lit.

You can see a fridge. What a letdown! The fridge is empty! If you haven't noticed it already, there seems to be something there by the wall, it's an oven. Make a note of this, you might have to put stuff on or in it later on. You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a table. On the table you can see a cookbook and a knife. What's that over there? It looks like it's a counter. Wow, isn't TextWorld just the best? But oh no! there's nothing on this piece of junk. You can see a stove. There's something about an object in a room that's just so... TextWorld. The stove is conventional. But the thing is empty, unfortunately. Aw, here you were, all excited for there to be things on it!

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
Well, here we are in the kitchen. The room is well lit.

You can see a fridge. What a letdown! The fridge is empty! If you haven't noticed it already, there seems to be something there by the wall, it's an oven. Make a note of this, you might have to put stuff on or in it later on. You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a table. On the table you can see a cookbook and a knife. What's that over there? It looks like it's a counter. Wow, isn't TextWorld just the best? But oh no! there's nothing on this piece of junk. You can see a stove. There's something about an object in a room that's just so... TextWorld. The stove is conventional. But the thing is empty, unfortunately. Aw, here you were, all excited for there to be things on it!
